{"type": "article", "id": 25459, "title": "Old Navy 新总裁上任，以及，Jimmy Choo 庆祝成立 20 周年｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-14T10:23:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1642, "name": "迪拜"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 4489, "name": "代言"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 6579, "name": "春夏系列"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 26246, "name": "Candie’s"}, {"id": 8914, "name": "Mr Porter"}, {"id": 4827, "name": "Ermenegildo Zegna"}, {"id": 26247, "name": "Not Just A Label"}, {"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104602Q6x9WpunljVFqv4h.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Gap-Inc-names-Sonia-Syngal-as-Old-Navy-head,681518.html#rc\"><b>Gap 集团任命 Old Navy 新总裁</b></a>｜Gap 集团任命 Sonia Syngal 为 Old Navy 新总裁，自上一任 Stefan Larsson 十月离职后一直空缺，后者跳槽至 Ralph Lauren 担任 CEO 。Sonia  在 Gap 已经工作有 12 年，最近刚升至全球供应链和产品经营部门执行副总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/PVH-Corp-completes-acquisition-of-its-Tommy-Hilfiger-China-JV,681367.html#rc\"><b>PVH 完成对 Tommy Hilfiger 中国公司收购</b></a>｜PVH 集团周三宣布完成对 Tommy Hilfiger 55% 股权以及中国合资公司的收购，这项收购二月时已经提出，预计在2016 年将增加约 1 亿美元的收入。 Tommy Hilfiger 一向是 PVH 旗下收益良好的品牌，2015 四季度收益上涨了 5% 且全年上涨了 4%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Not-Just-A-Label-teams-up-with-Dubai-Design-District,681391.html#rc\"><b>Not Just A Label 与迪拜设计区合作</b></a>｜独立设计师品牌平台 Not Just A Label 近日宣布与迪拜设计区 Dubai Design District (d3) 合作，支持阿联酋及国际上的创意人才。d3 将帮助 NJAL 与中东新兴的设计师合作交流及入驻后者的平台以带来全球的顾客，同时 NJAL 将帮助 d3 提供编辑、数码和网络化的机会。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/ermenegildo-zegna-mr-porter-e-commerce-10408149/\"><b>Ermenegildo Zegna 入驻电商 Mr Porter</b></a>｜意大利著名男装品牌 Ermenegildo Zegna 近日与奢侈品电商 Mr Porter 开始合作，后者将从 7 月 26 日首次开始售卖 Ermenegildo Zegna 成衣系列。1910 年创建，目前 Ermenegildo Zegna 在全球精品店、百货及其官网售卖，全球有 523 间门店。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/juniors/candies-sarah-hyland-creative-director-campaign-face-10408208/\"><b>Sarah Hyland 担任 Candie’s 创意总监</b></a>｜1981 年创立的服装品牌 Candie’s 一度是美国少女最喜爱的品牌，近日宣布将由 Sarah Hyland 出任品牌创意总监及新广告代言，值得一提的是，25 岁的 Hyland 并未有设计师履历，此前因出演美剧《摩登家庭》而走红。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104546lmzVos6bA1UXFEkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104547SiY8jEuI7CnJZbfm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">昨日我们报道过，Jimmy Choo 为庆祝成立 20 周年，推出 MEMENTO 系列，这一系列除了手绘概念图以外<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/jimmy-choo-20-year-anniversary-shoes-shop/\">有了更多实物图</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104548UZsjBtqGPD3TaN6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104548JkhKZaLTp2639cno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104549X1LrbQZjtNGwE4HM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104549S4DR7usfyXxPoBkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104550aT3f7knSHFypOmQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Vans 与威尼斯服装品牌 Summer Bummer <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/vans-summer-bummer-2016-shop/\">合作了一个新系列“it’s always summer somewhere”</a>，黑白为主调的背心、迷你裙、帆布鞋和凉鞋，在 Vans 官网可以购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104550S3JLt5OEQTXMzjU2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104550NSVBt9nQWPDYJ8db.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104551iYEHI18wkdgGFA6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104551pzDJSvACo758sO03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63157895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104552hrKCs9AmdJjo5Oqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104553tbdX6oyr38JWLcwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">日本品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/sacai-2016-spring-summer-campaign\"> Sacai 推出春夏季新广告</a>，设计师实验性的风格一览无余，以流行音乐文化为灵感：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104553VJKLDW7Z5SE60AaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104554xuQ7jU5tZIA9Blgi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045544ig02mshENtJTPZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/champion-reverse-weave-2016-spring-summer-collection\">Champion 发布 2016 春夏系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104555mFHz8cKBqjGIfskU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104555MBh23fsXucJym57i.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104556tqSai1G6OV3wvKnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104556Y9b2hzrGAgltXc1K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104557vd3wSmtiB4hgxCzW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104557zeKYOCsyZ7rIVhET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104558tXeJWEnuIHQGkSzh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">参加一些活动，比如婚礼、音乐节、排队什么的，总需要几套特定风格的服装，<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/topshop-summer-2016-party-dresses-shop/\">Topshop 最新的潮流指南“Dress Up and Go”</a> 精选品牌几套裙装供不同场合穿搭：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104558wJbXGY1KZ5iRkmoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104559ySeJoqgnuzjlGfL0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104559c3A9lYmM4L7F0eyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104600OA6sjd3gqv2TX8ek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104600mcFZrb5zsLNCMouR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104601CsuByGQSajrJqkKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}